<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
		<title>Matricule</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<style>
			* {
				color: #333;
			}
			.title {
				text-align: center;
			}
			h1 {
				text-transform: capitalize;
			}
		</style>
		{% block body %}
			<div class="title">
				<h1 style="margin: 0">- Request for Approval -</h1>
				<span>[ Matriculation Documentation ]</span>
			</div>
			<hr style="margin: 2rem 0"/>

			<h1 style="position: absolute; padding: 0 10px; bottom: 40%; left: 0">
				Radio
				<span style="background-color: #1f8bca; color: #fff; padding: 0 5px 5px 5px">
					Hub
				</span>
			</h1>

			<div class="content">
				<h3>
					<span style="font-size: 2rem">Dear</span>
					CEO,
				</h3>
				<h5></h5>
				<p>
					I am writing to seek your approval regarding the matriculation
										        documentation for
				</p>
				<center>
					<span>Email :
						<span style="text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 500">{{
            user.email | capitalize
          }}</span>
						| Matricule :
						<span style="
																              font-weight: 500;
																              color: white;
																              background-color: #333;
																              padding: 0 10px 5px 10px;
																            ">
							{% if doc is not null %}
								{{ doc.matricule }}
							{% else %}
								{{ rad.matcnom }}
							{% endif %}
						</span>
					</span>
				</center>
				<p>
					. Your feedback and endorsement on this matter are crucial before we
										        proceed further.
				</p>
			</div>
			<p>Best regards,</p>

		{% endblock %}
	</body>
</html>
